                <div class="tit_nav">
                    <span class="tit_l">您所在位置：</span><a href="/Home/Index">首页</a><b>></b><span>案例信息</span>
                </div>
                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/6022" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">CPGN-0190</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">7977 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">共患难易，同富贵难：宏图劳务成长之痛</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Bearing hardships together but not sharing blessings: the pain of Hongtu Labor growth</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">田玉英，吴倩倩</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中国石油大学（华东）</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">青岛宏图人力资源服务有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">服务业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">综合管理部门/总经理办公室</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">小微家族企业；共同创业；干股激励；盗取资源；家族式治理</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Small and micro family enterprises; co-entrepreneurship; dry stock incentive; theft of resources; family governance</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">当下，随着如火如荼的创业大潮不断升温，选择家族式自主创业的人越来越多。在小微家族式企业数量成爆炸式增长的同时，企业失败的案例也与日俱增。导致许多小公司纷纷倒下的原因，除了商业决策失误和市场竞争激烈外，家族式治理困境和创始合伙人之间的矛盾爆发也是重要原因。本案例以青岛宏图劳务公司创始人吴总的视角为切入点，描述了与早期合伙人王亮从风雨同舟的共同创业、赠送股权共同发展的快速成长到盗取共同资源，私创、同业企业的成长背叛之路，以此成为宏图劳务公司发展历程中的“剧痛”。希望通过阐释本案例，引导学生了解家族式治理模式究竟给宏图劳务公司带来了哪些弊端和风险隐患，同时让学员能够了解企业管理中人之贪婪和私欲膨胀给企业发展带来的致命一击，以及掌握小微家族企业中合伙人创业叛逃的具体原因，寻找规避与约束合伙人道德风险和逆向行为的科学方法，从而提高学员以后在小微家族式企业中的决策治理能力和识别与防范由主要合伙人背叛带来的经营风险的能力。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all"> At present, with the full tide of entrepreneurship warming up, more and more people choose to start family self-employment. While the number of small and micro family businesses has exploded, the cases of business failures are also growing. In addition to poor business decisions and fierce market competition, so are the plight of family governance and the outbreak of conflicts between founding partners. This case from the perspective of the founder of Qingdao Hongtu labor company as the breakthrough point, describes the early partner Wang Liang from joint venture, equity common growth to steal common resources, private creation, the growth of enterprise betrayal, to become the &quot;great pain&quot; in the development of Hongtu labor company. Hope to explain this case, guide students to understand the family governance model to grand labor company brings what disadvantages and risks, and let students can understand the greed and private expansion in enterprise management brings a fatal blow to enterprise development, and grasp the specific reasons of small family partners, to avoid and restrain partner moral risk and reverse behavior, so as to improve students in small micro family enterprise decision governance ability and the ability to identify and prevent business risks betrayed by main partners.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,博士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2020</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《公司治理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">家族式治理模式</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022-02</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">查看全文:</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/6022" target="_blank">点击查看</a></td>
                            </tr>
